message.body: Omg! What are you doing in Chicago? Lol

I thought I told you? The family I used to nanny for asked me to go out with them to help since they have 3 kids so I figured why the hell not since they are paying for my flight and room plus a paycheck haha
Honestly I'm not sold. I haven't seen anything great, I went to two museums and they both sucked. I tried to go to the Willis tower and there was Zero visibility of course.
No! Lol hope you're having fun!
I'm trying a blues place tonight
Oh wow! Really? Well I hope that doesn't disappoint.
Don't break any hearts Laura lol
Yeh I was a little upset about the whole thing, froze my butt off too haha... Oh I won't no worries haha
Aww lol how long will you be there for?
Just tomorrow. I felt yesterdays. I might have hyped it up in my head too much haha. They say it's nicer in summer and spring so maybe I'll come back
Bring me! Haha
Yes!! We will have so much more fun. I have southwest money I have to spend before Halloween
Lol awesome
We need to do new Orleans
Totally!
I'm dying to go. I just don't know if we should do Mardi Gras
Right I keep floating between are we missing the whole point of it if we don't go then and I hate people so maybe just a normal time
I could probably do without Mardi gras. Too many crazy drunk people lol
Yeah lol I feel like it's a good thing to see but I also hate people. Plus they'll price gouge just because it's Mardi gras
Oh god so true. So we will skip Mardi Gras haha. Just give me so shrimp gumbo
Haha sounds like a plan
We have so many plans. We haven't traveled together in a while. We have to do something
Definitely
You would love the steakhouse we went to last night. $50 filet mignon
Omg that's insane! Lol was it worth it?
In my opinion no. It was perfectly cooked but the flavor wasn't anything special and it came with nothing just a tiny bowl of soup or salad... I was fine with it because I didn't pay. It was her pick
That sucks lol it should have been amazing
Yeh I mean I think I've had better in philly
Figures lol
Philly is hard to beat lately because even these museums honestly sucked
That's disappointing
It really is. No wonder we were ranked 2nd best place to visit
True that lol
Fingers crossed blues is amazing. Somethings gotta give
I hope you enjoy it!
Ditto! I'm currently babysitting because today is her birthday and they are at dinner. So I'm going to head out later tonight.
Have fun :)
Thank you thank you! Esther just cried for about 20 minutes so I'm Definitely ready haha
Haha I'm sure
Are you a fan of uber?
